FT  17 SEP 94 / UK Company News: Quebecor ends offer talks with Hunterprint
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By PAUL TAYLOR
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Quebecor, the Canadian publishing and forestry group, has ended its
discussions with Hunterprint, the lossmaking UK printer.
